  <official_title>Phase I Study to Investigate the Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacodynamic Effects of Sublingual Immunotherapy Tablets Given in Single Rising Doses and in Multi Dose Regimens to Subjects With an Allergy to Ragweed Pollen.</official_title>
