  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the safety and tolerability of several doses of
      ragweed pollen allergen extract administered as sublingual tablets in subjects with allergic
      rhinitis to ragweed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
